m all evil: the Lord shall keep thy soul.","searchKeywords":["may","the","lord","preserve","thee","from","all","evil","shall","keep","thy","soul"]},{"verseId":"brenton_psalms_120_8","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":24,"bookName":"Psalms","bookAbbrev":"psalms","chapter":120,"verse":8,"text":"The Lord shall keep thy coming in, and thy going out, from henceforth and even for ever.","searchKeywords":["the","lord","shall","keep","thy","coming","and","going","out","from","henceforth","even","for","ever"]}]